Docs.example:
Bad example:

public long Bad (int a, int b)
{
	// e.g. Bad (Int32.MaxInt, Int32.MaxInt) == 1
	return a * b;
}

Good example:

public long Good (int a, int b)
{
	// e.g. Good (Int32.MaxInt, Int32.MaxInt) == 4611686014132420609
	return (long) a * b;
}

